code: export const START_TAG="%START_SNIPPET%";export const END_TAG="%END_SNIPPET%";export const parseSnippet=source=>{const[pre,textAndPost]=source.indexOf(START_TAG)!==-1?source.split(START_TAG):["",source];const[text,post]=textAndPost.indexOf(END_TAG)!==-1?textAndPost.split(END_TAG):[textAndPost,""];return{pre,post,text};};
